143
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,840
Gu Yixiao, let me out of here.

144
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,040
You're not going anywhere.

145
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,280
Ye Xingwan,

146
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:18,840
you've told me so many things.

147
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,800
Which of them were real?

148
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:20,640
