♪It taught me to stay silent first♪

156
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:12,260
♪So the explosion would be deafening♪

157
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:19,340
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

158
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:22,460
♪The stubborn pain♪

159
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:29,140
♪Hardens into the hottest flame♪

160
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:35,820
