don't ask for my mercy♪

161
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:39,260
♪Just enjoy this searing pain♪

162
00:11:39,380 --> 00:11:42,620
♪See whether blood or tears flow first♪

163
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:45,500
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

164
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:49,940
♪Greed caused the chaos,
